      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELEGANT ZEPHYR (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.77 beating Zing Matilda. Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. Expected to be right there at the finish again. SLIM RUSTY (4) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 10 length sixth (20.20) at this track in a Best 8. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Key chance on best form. OUR BELLA ROSE (6) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (19.74) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Has good early speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Has ability and can measure up. CHICKEN KNIGHT (8) has strong credentials from this draw.",
